name: Double Trouble
description:
A tribute piece to one of the most respected and influential Indonesian illustrators, Arya Mularama aka Gogoporen. Been eyeing on his comical works for a long time and adoring the playful blue bear so much.

So I decided to summon my black catto and asked him to play along with Gogo. They did. But (unexpectedly) also made a lot of mess here and there. Oops. Not my fault.
